  <brief_title>The Efficacy of Color-Doppler Ultrasonography to Assess the Renal Blood Flow With the Estimation of GFR</brief_title>
  <official_title>Color-Doppler Ultrasonography vs 99mTc-DTPA Scintigraphy to Assess the Renal Blood Flow</official_title>
